==English==

===Noun===
'''bowleg'''
#A [[leg]] that [[curve]]s [[outward]] at the [[knee]]. It might refer to the leg of a human, animal or even a piece of furniture. For humans this deformity is formally called [[genu varum]].

===Derived terms===
*[[bow-legged]]

==== Synonyms ====
*[[bandy]], [[bandy-legged]]
*[[genu varum]], [[tibia vara]], [[valgus]] deformity

